The '''2014 [[Open du Pays d'Aix]]''' was a professional [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Clay courts|clay courts]]. It was the first edition of the tournament which was part of the [[2014 ATP Challenger Tour]]. It took place in [[Aix-en-Provence]], [[France]] between 5 and 11 May 2014.

