===Other entrants===
The following players received wildcards into the singles main draw:
* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Axel Michon]]
* {{flagicon|FRA}} Julien Obry
* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Florent Serra]]
* {{flagicon|FRA}} Martin Vaisse

The following players received entry from the qualifying draw:
* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jonathan Eysseric]]
* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Laurent Lokoli]]
* {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Yann Marti]]
* {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Henri Laaksonen]]

The following players received entry as a lucky loser:
* {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Jordi Samper Montaña]]

